## Formatting
- When writing LaTeX in Jaz markdown, use `\(...\)` for inline math and `\[...\]` for display math. Put display equations on their own lines. Do not use raw single-dollar math like `$x$`; single-dollar text is treated literally so file paths, variables, and links with `$` render correctly. If needed, block `$$ ... $$` is also acceptable for standalone display equations.
